Opie & Jim Norton OCT 20 2015 Tue (03:06:20)



On Today's Show:

JIM BREUER & JEFF DANIELS.

They talk about Amy Schumer getting shit because some people think she stole some jokes on her new HBO special. Jim Breuer joins them in the studio. They cover things like the Mets, his family, and his upcoming rock album and tour. Jeff Daniels joins them. They talk about his new movie about Steve Jobs and some of his other gigs
